</header>

<div class="slider">
    <form action="/auth" method="get">
        <button class="authButton" type="submit">Find Recipes!</button>
    </form>
    <div class="title">
        <img class="logo" src="/images/FLAVOUR (1).png">
    </div>
   
    
    <div class="images">
        <div class="item" style="--i: 1;">
            <img src="/images/1.png">
        </div>
        <div class="item" style="--i: 2;">
            <img src="/images/2.png">
        </div>
        <div class="item" style="--i: 3;">
            <img src="/images/3.png">
        </div>
        <div class="item" style="--i: 4;">
            <img src="/images/4.png">
        </div>
        <div class="item" style="--i: 5;">
            <img src="/images/5.png">
        </div>
        <div class="item" style="--i: 6;">
            <img src="/images/6.png">
        </div>
    </div>
   
    <div class="content">
        <div class="item active">
            <h1>Chocolate Cake</h1>
            <div class="des">
                Moist, Rich, and Basically a Chocolate Hug🤎 <br>
                Moist, fluffy, and layered with deep chocolate flavor – this classic chocolate cake is a celebration in every slice. Perfect for birthdays, date nights, or those ‘just because’ cravings.
            </div>
            
        </div>
        <div class="item">
            <h1>Pancakes</h1>
            <div class="des">
                Pancakes So Good, You’ll Skip the Snooze Button! ⏰💛<br>
                Golden on the outside, soft and airy on the inside – these classic pancakes are a breakfast dream come true. Just add syrup and smiles!
            </div>
            
        </div>
        <div class="item">
            <h1> Grilled Salmon Salad</h1>
            <div class="des">
                Fresh, Flavorful, and Totally Omega-mazing! 🧡🥗<br>
                Juicy grilled salmon meets crisp greens, creamy avocado, and a zesty lemon vinaigrette – this salad is light, refreshing, and bursting with flavor.
            </div>
            
        </div>
        <div class="item">
            <h1>Pizza</h1>
            <div class="des">
                Homemade Pizza, Pizzeria Vibes! 🍽️🏠<br>
                Colorful, crunchy, and bursting with fresh flavor – this loaded veggie pizza is a garden party on a crust.
            </div>
           
        </div>
        <div class="item">
            <h1>Chicken Curry</h1>
            <div class="des">
                This Chicken Curry is What Dreams (and Dinners) Are Made Of! 😍🍛<br>
                Juicy chicken simmered in a rich, spiced gravy made with onions, tomatoes, and aromatic masalas – this classic curry brings warmth and tradition to your plate.
            </div>
            
        </div>
        <div class="item">
            <h1>Spaghetti</h1>
            <div class="des">
                This spaghetti’s got sauce, style, and serious flavor swagger! 😎✨<br>
                Simple, soulful, and saucy – this classic spaghetti is a weeknight wonder packed with rich tomato flavor and a hint of garlic. Ready in minutes, loved for a lifetime!
            </div>
            
        </div>
       
    </div>
    <button id="prev"><</button>
    <button id="next">></button>
</div>

<script src="app.js"></script>
</body>